                        width="200"><br><br><br>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title" style="text-align: center;">WHAT IS OUR PROJECT</h5>
                        <p class="card-text" style="text-align: center;">We have created a stock exchanging website that
                            uses real-time price on both stocks
                            and currencies. We also have various features like showing whether the prices have gone up
                            or dropped down, graphs to easily display
                            and understand the price differences, and also a portfolio page to see which stocks have
                            been purchased and how much profit has been made.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
